comments: Class material sucks and can be difficult if you\'re not a CIS major. Vance is cool tho - he\'s funny and super helpful.Tests/quizzes are open book. Key to success is to make friends and do your homework in the lab during the TA hours and you\'ll ace all the homework. Choose a good group for the final project and you\'ll do well. I def recommend him.
I personally disliked him...he\'s a real sarcastic guy and he can get on your nerves pretty quickly. As far as the class difficulty goes...it\'s pretty easy. Pick a good group and you\'ll be fine.
